# Basis Lead System

Lead management system built with Django, PostgreSQL, Redis and Celery.

## 🚀 Stack
- Django
- PostgreSQL
- Redis
- Celery
- Docker & Docker Compose
- Telegram Bot (aiogram)

## 🏗 Architecture
- Web service (Gunicorn)
- Bot service
- PostgreSQL database
- Redis message broker
- Celery worker

## ⚡ Features
- Lead collection via Telegram bot
- Hot lead detection
- Async background processing
- Admin dashboard

## 🐳 Run locally

docker-compose up --build

Open:
http://localhost:8000

## 🔐 Security
Environment variables stored in .env
.env is excluded from git
